These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-3-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: water, almond-milk, coffee, hot-chocolate, fanta, tea, mirinda
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
2. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking water is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
7. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
9. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |  3   |   4    |    5     |    6     |  7  |
| Beverage   | tea | hot-chocolate | almond-milk | mirinda | fanta | coffee | water |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-3-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  nurse, accountant, fisherman, police-officer, dancer, project-manager, entrepreneur
1. the project-manager is on the left or right of the nurse##3
2. the accountant is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
3. the nurse is on the right of the dancer##1
4. the project-manager is on the far right##1
5. the entrepreneur is on the left or right of the police-officer##3
6. the police-officer is on the left of the dancer##1
7. the police-officer is on the left of the dancer##1
8. the accountant is between the entrepreneur and the fisherman##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |    2     |      3       |      4      |      5       |  6   |   7   |
| Job   | fisherman | accountant | entrepreneur | police-officer | dancer | nurse | project-manager |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-3-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: british, dutch, pakistani, japanese, malaysian, thai, german
1. the dutch is on the far left or far right##3
2. the british is between the dutch and the malaysian##2
3. the malaysian is on the right of the british##1
4. the british is on the left or right of the dutch##3
5. the german is on the left of the thai##1
6. the german is between the pakistani and the thai##2
7. the thai is on the left or right of the japanese##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |     4      |    5    |   6    |    7     |
| Nationality   | dutch | british | malaysian | pakistani | german | thai | japanese |

