.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: techno, blues, disco, gospel, funk, salsa, rock
1. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
2. the fan of funk is on the right of the fan of techno##1
3. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of blues##1
4. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
5. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
6. the fan of funk is in the middle##1
7. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |   2    |    3    |  4  |   5   |    6    |    7    |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | rock | techno | funk | gospel | disco | blues |

