.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-3-5::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: chess, reading, baking, singing, cooking, drawing, camping
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person who's hobby is chess##2
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
6. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |    4    |       5       |    6    |    7    |
| Hobby   | cooking | reading | singing | camping | drawing | baking | chess |

