4. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left or far right##3
5. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of folk##1
6. the fan of pop is between the fan of salsa and the fan of dubstep##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |   3   |  4  |  5   |   6    |   7    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | folk | dubstep | pop | salsa | indie | electronic |

