5. the fan of techno is between the fan of disco and the fan of soul##2
6. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of techno##1
7. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
8. the fan of punk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2  |  3  |   4   |  5   |     6     |    7    |
| Music-Genre   | punk | d&b | soul | techno | disco | gospel | folk |

 